text: Whitehorse East was a territorial electoral district in the Canadian territory of Yukon, which was represented on the Yukon Territorial Council from 1952 to 1974. The district comprised the eastern portion of the territorial capital, Whitehorse. ==Representatives== {| class="wikitable" |- ! Name ! Took Office !
